{"tid":1655512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"LBJ 說言論自由","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T08:25:10.000Z","uid":296283,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e25ad2b7461eb3c5d9f172efd6cbda1ba75d75","tid":1655512,"uid":296283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"湖人球星勒邦占士（LeBron James）周一首度就火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）早前在Twitter表態支持香港的反政府示威者一事開腔，認為莫利在表態之前並未對有關情況掌握足夠資訊。<br />\n<br />\nLBJ周一在湖人對勇士的季前賽之前被問到有關事件時表示︰「是的，我們有言論自由，但有時候，當你沒想及其他人而只想到自己，便可能產生負面影響。」<br />\n<br />\n占士說︰「我不想與莫利發生口頭爭執，但我認為他表態前對有關情況並未掌握足夠資訊。很多人因而受到傷害，不止是經濟，還有身體、情感和精神上。所以我們發推文、說甚麼和做甚麼都必須小心，儘管是我們有言論自由，但亦有可能因而帶來很多負面影響。」<br />\n<br />\n占士補充道，他和隊友們一直保持沉默是因為他們對該狀況沒有足夠資訊，而他並非要批判聯盟如何處理這情況，他說︰「我只是認為，當你被誤導或對一些事情沒有足夠的教育，而我只是談到那推文本身，你永不會知道可能發生的後果。我們全都看到這事，不止是對我們聯賽，還有對我們所有在美國的人、對在中國的人亦一樣。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60155256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60155256&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9MFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=cfaac53e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191015%26s%3D7032049%26a%3D60155256&h=9ae5c50d\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191015&amp;s=7032049&amp;a=60155256</a>"},{"pid":"4c2ad4f11cb482e877d42c58b9446ee7349f7eda","tid":1655512,"uid":25321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"Lickbeijing就有佢份"},{"pid":"808825a1b85841e0891ce9e52a675c00a528cd3d","tid":1655512,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c2ad4f11cb482e877d42c58b9446ee7349f7eda","tid":1655512,"uid":25321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"Lickbeijing就有佢份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:01:50.000Z","msg":"Lick Beijing James<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f800e7e2857061a23bbe8bd6332356e45a497f","tid":1655512,"uid":46966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:02:01.000Z","msg":"不少美國網友紛紛批評詹姆斯向中國低頭，還有人挖出去年詹姆斯在美國黑人民權運動領袖馬丁路德金恩（Martin Luther King Jr.）逝世50週年當天，在推特上PO出名言，「任何地方的不公不義，都威脅著所有地方的公平正義」、「當我們對重要的事變得沉默，我們人生便開始失去價值。」文末並標籤「謝謝你馬丁路德金恩50」，這則推文如今看起來格外諷刺。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d02f62288a69ed278e24142a75482d8c11ef1b","tid":1655512,"uid":296283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"在一個這麼自由的地方說這些說話！<br />\n<br />\n你老味臭閪，你老祖都係做黑奴⋯⋯你老母臭閪冇理由唔明白自由嘅可貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3f64fae24b48e1f6915ef54b014d2be23b9e80","tid":1655512,"uid":10524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:25:10.000Z","msg":"今晚有冇手足燒Lick Beijing James 波衫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655754</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}